{"tid":660051,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"希望你可以早日放低","createTime":"2018-05-10T11:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T13:31:41.000Z","uid":8380,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"deb16e54745b9867bc5052d35a2ff274da8c19ec","tid":660051,"uid":8380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:07:24.000Z","msg":"啱啱同你分手，我呢幾日都係咁喊，喊到眼都腫埋，但係一覺瞓醒就諗通咗。可能我地真係性格不合，一齊嗰陣我成日就住就住咁，但又唔同你講，最後一次過爆發，亦都返唔到轉頭。我希望你可以早日放低我，揾到一個比我更好更愛你嘅人，一個鍾意真正嘅你嘅人。<br />\n多謝你令我嘅世界變得更精彩！<br />\n希望你睇到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地有咩想同ex講？"},{"pid":"d4db89be729dd163fe2d5613cdb12dcb64724cb2","tid":660051,"uid":8380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"所有你送嘅嘢，仲有同你一齊影嘅相，我會好好保存，因為有你，我先有呢段咁好嘅回憶。"},{"pid":"80c455b427c9030127c184a57fb72885d929a72d","tid":660051,"uid":88884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:27:58.000Z","msg":"你幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700f5faa51f46e7a7398ab4deb175c1480dfd374","tid":660051,"uid":53691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"點解咁就放棄我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}